TITLE: Complete Dockerfile for Python Apify Actor
DESCRIPTION: A complete Dockerfile for a Python Actor. It uses the Apify Python base image, installs dependencies from requirements.txt, and copies the source code. It includes a CMD instruction to specify how to run the Actor.
