TITLE: Extracting Hourly Weather Data from BBC Weather Page
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet extracts hourly weather data from the BBC Weather page, including datetime and temperature information, and appends it to a list of weather data.
SOURCE: https://github.com/apify/apify-docs/blob/master/sources/academy/tutorials/python/scrape_data_python.md#2025-04-18_snippet_6

