TITLE: Filtering Amazon Product Data
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of filtering logic using Array.reduce() to process Amazon product data and find lowest prices per ASIN.
SOURCE: https://github.com/apify/apify-docs/blob/master/sources/academy/platform/expert_scraping_with_apify/solutions/integrating_webhooks.md#2025-04-18_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const filtered = items.reduce((acc, curr) => {
    const prevPrice = acc?.[curr.asin] ? +acc[curr.asin].offer.slice(1) : null;
    const price = +curr.offer.slice(1);

    if (!acc[curr.asin] || prevPrice > price) acc[curr.asin] = curr;

    return acc;
}, {});
```

