TITLE: Using Apify SDK's Built-in saveSnapshot Utility with Puppeteer
DESCRIPTION: A complete example of an Apify Actor that navigates to a URL specified in the input and saves a screenshot using the built-in puppeteerUtils.saveSnapshot function. This demonstrates the recommended approach for debugging Puppeteer-based crawlers.
