TITLE: Creating an ASPX Form Submission Utility Function in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: A utility function for Web Scraper that handles form submission on ASP.NET pages. The function serializes form data, adds submit button information, and manages AJAX posts for proper navigation through .ASPX pages.
