TITLE: JSON Response Format for Rate Limit Exceeded
DESCRIPTION: Example JSON response when a client exceeds the API rate limit of requests per second. The API endpoints respond with HTTP status code 429 and this error message structure.
SOURCE: https://github.com/apify/apify-docs/blob/master/sources/platform/storage/usage.md#2025-04-18_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
    "error": {
        "type": "rate-limit-exceeded",
        "message": "You have exceeded the rate limit of ... requests per second"
    }
}
```

